data.description: Opportunity to own a fully renovated historic home in Fox Park! This home was extensively updated in 2018 with the modern features you wish for (updated windows, electrical, zoned HVAC, and plumbing) in the historic neighborhood you must have. The main floor offers a large flexible open concept layout while maintaining room designation. Impossible to miss the hardwood floors and custom crown molding with a tasteful kitchen design, large center island, and pantry. Upstairs you will find 2 large guest bedrooms, guest bath with double vanity sink, and the coveted second floor laundry room. The back of the home is owners oasis, with a four piece bathroom, jetted soaking tub, walk in closet, and private balcony overlooking fenced in backyard and a 2-car garage port. All of this on a quiet dead end city street with friendly neighbors just one block from Fox Park! Enjoy this amazing tight nit community with wonderful community activities and restaurants right out your front door!
